The Discovery Channel&amp;#039;s groundbreaking program uses cutting edge technology--the very same that George Lucas used in making 1999&amp;#039;s THE PHANTOM MENACE--to recreate the prehistoric world. Utilizing CGI special effects to bring dinosaurs to life, WHEN DINOSAURS ROAMED AMERICA is appealing to viewers of all ages, as scientifically accurate as it is entertaining.

